<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <i>Ravaging the Vulnerable: Abuses Against Persons at High Risk of HIV Infection in Bangladesh</i>, <a href="/wiki/Human_Rights_Watch" title="Human Rights Watch">Human Rights Watch</a>, August 2003. <a href="http://www.hrw.org/reports/2003/bangladesh0803/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.hrw.org/reports/2003/bangladesh0803/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Report online</a>.<br />
See also: <a href="http://www.altlawforum.org/PUBLICATIONS/PUCL%20REPORT%202003" class="external text" title="http://www.altlawforum.org/PUBLICATIONS/PUCL%20REPORT%202003" rel="nofollow">Peoples Union of Civil Liberties (Karnataka) Report on Human Rights Violations Against the Transgender Community</a>, released in September 2003. Reported in <a href="http://www.countercurrents.org/gen-narrain141003.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.countercurrents.org/gen-narrain141003.htm" rel="nofollow">Being a Eunuch</a>, By Siddarth Narrain, for Frontline, 14 October, 2003.</li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://soniafaleiro.blogspot.com/2005/10/dying-of-evening-stars-vi.html" class="external text" title="http://soniafaleiro.blogspot.com/2005/10/dying-of-evening-stars-vi.html" rel="nofollow">The Dying of The Evening Stars VI</a>, by Sonia Faleiro. Published in <a href="/wiki/Tehelka" title="Tehelka">Tehelka</a>, October 28, 2005.</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.thebody.com/unaids/wac/wac2001_posters/bios/mausi.html" class="external text" title="http://www.thebody.com/unaids/wac/wac2001_posters/bios/mausi.html" rel="nofollow">"Shabnam Mausi"</a>. <i>The Body</i>. December 2001<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.thebody.com/unaids/wac/wac2001_posters/bios/mausi.html" class="external free" title="http://www.thebody.com/unaids/wac/wac2001_posters/bios/mausi.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.thebody.com/unaids/wac/wac2001_posters/bios/mausi.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on June 5</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Shabnam+Mausi&amp;rft.atitle=The+Body&amp;rft.date=December+2001&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebody.com%2Funaids%2Fwac%2Fwac2001_posters%2Fbios%2Fmausi.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hijra_(South_Asia)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.geocities.com/miss_malika/ShabnamMausi.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/miss_malika/ShabnamMausi.htm" rel="nofollow">"Shabnam Mausi"</a>. <i>Malika's Indian Transgender Palace</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.geocities.com/miss_malika/ShabnamMausi.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.geocities.com/miss_malika/ShabnamMausi.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.geocities.com/miss_malika/ShabnamMausi.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on June 5</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Shabnam+Mausi&amp;rft.atitle=Malika%27s+Indian+Transgender+Palace&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geocities.com%2Fmiss_malika%2FShabnamMausi.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hijra_(South_Asia)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
